---
import astroLogo from '../assets/astro.svg';
import background from '../assets/background.svg';
---

<div class="hero min-h-screen bg-base-200 relative overflow-hidden">
	<img class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-20" src={background.src} alt="" fetchpriority="high" />
	<div class="hero-content text-center">
		<div class="max-w-md">
			<div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
				<a href="https://astro.build" class="inline-block">
					<img src={astroLogo.src} width="115" height="48" alt="Astro Homepage" class="transition-transform hover:scale-105" />
				</a>
			</div>
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Astro UI 演示项目</h1>
			<p class="py-4 text-lg">
				这是一个基于 Astro、Tailwind CSS 和 DaisyUI 的演示项目，展示了如何使用现代UI库美化你的Astro应用。
			</p>
			<div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 mt-6">
				<a class="btn btn-primary" href="/guide">Astro 基础指南</a>
				<a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/demo">组件演示</a>
				<a href="https://docs.astro.build/zh-cn/" class="btn btn-outline btn-accent">
					官方文档
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"></path><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"></line></svg>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="fixed bottom-8 right-8 z-10">
		<a href="https://astro.build/blog/astro-5/" class="card card-compact w-80 bg-base-100 shadow-xl card-hover">
			<div class="card-body">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
					<svg width="32" height="32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="text-primary">
						<path
							d="M24.667 12c1.333 1.414 2 3.192 2 5.334 0 4.62-4.934 5.7-7.334 12C18.444 28.567 18 27.456 18 26c0-4.642 6.667-7.053 6.667-14Zm-5.334-5.333c1.6 1.65 2.4 3.43 2.4 5.333 0 6.602-8.06 7.59-6.4 17.334C13.111 27.787 12 25.564 12 22.666c0-4.434 7.333-8 7.333-16Zm-6-5.333C15.111 3.555 16 5.556 16 7.333c0 8.333-11.333 10.962-5.333 22-3.488-.774-6-4-6-8 0-8.667 8.666-10 8.666-20Z"
							fill="currentColor"></path>
					</svg>
					<h2 class="card-title">Astro 5.0 新特性</h2>
				</div>
				<p>
					从内容层到服务器岛屿，点击了解Astro 5.0中的新功能和改进。
				</p>
				<div class="card-actions justify-end">
					<button class="btn btn-sm btn-primary">了解更多</button>
				</div>
			</div>
		</a>
	</div>
</div>
